yatsuhi-no-Kami|ja|大綾津日神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ō-Ayatsuhi-no-Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 禍津日神}} (considered identical to Ō-Magatsuhi-no-Kami).
